item.title: Sugbot
item.description: A news bot built for sharing the most recent news from local news agencies. News are fetched via RSS feeds.

item.title: Dikto
item.description: A dictionary website built using Angular. It uses external APIs from Wordnik, Merriam-Webster, and Google Translate API.

item.title: TOEIC Web System
item.description: A system where Japanese TOEIC-exam takers can study, review, and take quizzes to prepare for their exams.
